# Async Readability

- Declare async functions with the `async` keyword (no hidden async behavior).
- Prefer `await` over chaining `.then()` for async calls.

```typescript
// ❌ BAD
const loadUser = () => fetchUser().then((res) => res.data);

// ✅ GOOD
const loadUser = async () => {
  const res = await fetchUser();
  return res.data;
};
```
